# Offers – List Offers (Admin)
# Smoke tests for GET /offers.
#
# Admin-only endpoint. Supports optional filtering by status, merchant_id,
# and date range, plus standard pagination (page / page_size).
# Run the helper login requests below to obtain a fresh token.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001/api/v1

# Paste fresh tokens here (use helper login requests below).
# These placeholder values are expired local-dev tokens from seed data — never real credentials.
@adminToken = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoiZDlmNGIzYzItNmI1Yy01ZDRlLTdjM2ItNmE1ZTRkM2MyYjFhIiwidXNlcl9yb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJleHAiOjE3NzI1NTY4MDN9.nS9C2SjsN7cgVRBkAto4iIiW_8gpJdPRMS-xfmaHoWQ
@userToken  = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoiYjdlMmMxYTItNGYzYS00ZTJiLTljMWEtOGQyZTNmNGI1YzZkIiwidXNlcl9yb2xlIjoidXNlciIsImV4cCI6MTc3MjU1NDgzM30.JNCPlr5qJ_pbxawd0IRTpO3SHceuGgBLFnNvXC8tU7I

### Helper – obtain a fresh admin token (carol)
# Returns access_token — paste as "Bearer <token>" into @adminToken above.
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "carol@clicknback.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass"
}

### Helper – obtain a fresh user token (alice)
# Returns access_token — paste as "Bearer <token>" into @userToken above.
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@clicknback.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass"
}

### 200 – Happy path: list all offers (first page, default page size)
# Expected: paginated envelope with data[], pagination.total, pagination.offset=0, pagination.limit=20.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: explicit pagination (offset=0, limit=5)
# Verifies the envelope shape with a non-default limit.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?offset=0&limit=5
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: second page (verifies pagination slicing)
# Verifies offset=5 skips the first 5 results.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?offset=5&limit=5
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: filter by status=active
# Expected: only offers with status=active; total reflects active count.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=active
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: filter by status=inactive
# Expected: only offers with status=inactive.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=inactive
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: filter yields empty result set (offset beyond total)
# Expected: {"data": [], "pagination": {"offset": 990, "limit": 20, "total": <N>}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=inactive&offset=990
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: filter by merchant_id
# Expected: only offers belonging to the specified merchant.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?merchant_id=a1b2c3d4-e5f6-4a7b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: filter by date range (overlapping offers)
# Returns offers whose validity window intersects [date_from, date_to].
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?date_from=2026-01-15&date_to=2026-01-30
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: filter by date_from only (open-ended)
# Returns offers ending on or after date_from.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?date_from=2026-12-01
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: combine status + merchant_id filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=active&merchant_id=a1b2c3d4-e5f6-4a7b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: combine all supported filters in one request
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=active&merchant_id=a1b2c3d4-e5f6-4a7b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d&date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-12-31
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 400 – Sad path: invalid status value
# Expects validation error; only "active" and "inactive" are valid.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=pending
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 400 – Sad path: date_from is after date_to
# Cross-field validator rejects the incoherent date range.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?date_from=2026-12-31&date_to=2026-01-01
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 400 – Sad path: multiple simultaneous violations (invalid status + inverted dates)
# Both validators fire; expects a combined validation error response.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?status=invalid&date_from=2026-12-31&date_to=2026-01-01
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 422 – Sad path: malformed merchant_id (not a UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?merchant_id=not-a-uuid
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 422 – Sad path: offset below minimum (offset=-1)
# Schema validator enforces offset >= 0.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers?offset=-1
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 401 – Sad path: missing authentication
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers

### 403 – Sad path: authenticated as a non-admin user
# alice has role=user; expects 403 FORBIDDEN.
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers
Authorization: {{userToken}}
